title: Ike's Place - SF
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, American, Fast food, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Casual sandwich shop offering also many vegetarian and vegan sandwiches using various faux meats like tofurkey, breaded chickn pattie, meatball; has vegan daiya cheese. The wheat bread might contain honey - ask. Busy at lunch time. Current location since summer 2012; previously at 2247 Market St as reported to Happycow.
